task.summary: Created Guess-number-game using Spring - created the pom.xml files - created beans.xml - created various game classes with respective dependencies - used Spring and xml for setter and constructor-based dependency injection - removed beans.xml and created AppConfig with annotations - used Spring annotations for local fields with .properties file - removed field annotations and used constructor-based dependency injection (removed AppConfig and only use GameConfig) - set up Project lombok in project

[Guess-the-number-game] add Spring boot to the existing project - parent pom.xml -> remove all dependencies, build plugins, & properties (excl java) -> add parent tag - org.springframework.boot & <relativepath/>
- core.xml -> remove all dependencies excl lombok -> add spring-boot-starter dependency -> remove libs folder
- logback.xml -> rename to logback-spring.xml -> add <include..../> -> set spring logging to INFO
-console.xml -> add build plugin for spring boot maven
- console -> add application.properties to rss folder -> Main.class -> add @SpringBootApplication, remove context code & add SpringApplication.run()
